    "title": "Crompton Greaves is Hiring: Quality Control Engineer (Mid-Level)",
    "description": "We at Crompton Greaves are looking for an experienced Quality Control Engineer based out of Srinagar. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Crompton Greaves:\nCrompton Greaves is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Crompton Greaves!",
